## 仮定の確認


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# 正規性の検定
check_normality(fit_lm)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
OK: residuals appear as normally distributed (p = 0.198).
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# 等分散性の検定
check_homogeneity(fit_lm)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
OK: There is not clear evidence for different variances across groups (Bartlett Test, p = 0.729).
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# 異分散性の検定
check_heteroscedasticity(fit_lm)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
OK: Error variance appears to be homoscedastic (p = 0.832).
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# モデル診断
check_model(fit_lm)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](2_ANOVAとカテゴリカル変数のコーディング_files/figure-html/check-assumptions-1.png){width=3600}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# DHARMaによる残差診断
DHARMa::simulateResiduals(fittedModel = fit_lm, n = 500) |> 
plot()
```

